text: A-Leagues is an umbrella term that refers to several Australian and New Zealand professional soccer competitions. These are: * The A-League Men, the highest professional league for men (used to be called the A-League) * The A-League Women, the highest professional league for women (used to be called the W-League) * The A-League Youth, the highest professional league for youth (used to be called the Y-League)
title: A-Leagues
